name: Crypto Snake Play #13
description:
Crypto Snake is a collection of 20 unique handmade pixel art plays of the iconic game “snake”.
Each play has only one edition.
Each play increases the snake size according to the eaten blocks.
The blocks start at 1 and increase by 1 in each play.
It was created in a 32x32 px image, and exported to 1080x1080 px.

Play        # 13
Snake size  # 82
Block size  # 13
